'''砷酸二氢钾'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为KH<sub>2</sub>AsO<sub>4</sub>。它可由[[碳酸钾|碳酸钾]]和[[五氧化二砷|五氧化二砷]]在水中反应制得。<ref name=Dickson>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica|volume=3|issue=1|issn=0365-110X|date=1950-01-01|pages=6–9|doi=10.1107/S0365110X50000021|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0365110X50000021|title=The hydrogen bond in crystals. VIII. The isotope effect in KH<sub>2</sub>AsO<sub>4</sub>|accessdate=2021-03-26|author=D. H. W. Dickson, A. R. Ubbelohde|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603105708/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0365110X50000021|dead-url=no}}</ref>

砷酸二氢钾在400 °C分解，生成偏砷酸钾。<ref name=Dickson />它和[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]在pH 7.2~8时反应，可以得到KH<sub>2</sub>AsO<sub>3</sub>S。<ref>Rakhimov, K.; Zhigarnovskii, B. M.; Polyakov, Yu. A.; Bugakov, V. I.; Orlovskii, V. P.; Kozhenkov, V. Yu.; Abdullaeva, M. I. Synthesis and investigation of the physicochemical properties of hydrothioarsenates of potassium, rubidium, and cesium{{ru}}. ''Izvestiya Akademii Nauk SSSR, Neorganicheskie Materialy'', 1987. 23 (10): 1691-1695. ISSN: 0002-337X.</ref>它和[[三氟化锑|三氟化锑]]反应，可以得到K(SbF<sub>2</sub>)HAsO<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=578|issue=1|language=de|issn=0044-2313|date=1989|pages=133–142|doi=10.1002/zaac.19895780115|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/zaac.19895780115|title=Verbindungen des Antimon(III) mit SbFnOm-Koordinationsspähre Kristallstrukturen von K(SbF<sub>2</sub>)HAsO<sub>4</sub>, NH<sub>4</sub>(SbF<sub>2</sub>)HAsO<sub>4</sub> und Sb<sub>3</sub>O<sub>2</sub>F<sub>5</sub>|accessdate=2021-03-26|author=K. Holz, R. Mattes}}</ref>它和[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]（40%）发生放热反应，生成K[AsF<sub>5</sub>OH]。<ref>{{cite book|location=Hoboken, NJ, USA|language=en|isbn=9781118409466|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc.|date=2012-10-14|pages=117–120|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/9781118409466.ch20|title=Fluoro and Fluorohydroxy Complexes of As, Sb, and Sn|accessdate=2021-03-26|editor=Herbert W. Roesky|author=Lothar Kolditz|doi=10.1002/9781118409466.ch20}}</ref>它和镁盐在溶液中反应，形成KMgAsO<sub>4</sub>·6H<sub>2</sub>O沉淀。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=640|issue=15|language=en|date=2014-12|pages=3177–3183|doi=10.1002/zaac.201400265|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/zaac.201400265|title=Preparation, Structural, Thermogravimetric and Spectroscopic Study of Magnesium Potassium Arsenate Hexahydrate: Preparation of Magnesium Potassium Arsenate Hexahydrate|accessdate=2021-03-26|author=Zuldjevat Abdija, Metodija Najdoski, Violeta Koleva, Tomče Runčevski, Robert E. Dinnebier, Bojan Šoptrajanov, Viktor Stefov}}</ref>

